    {
      "id": "69a89592_fc9bc0d3",
      "file_path": "scripts/policy/get-versions.sh",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 61,
      "message": "suggestion: instead of cloning the whole project, could just retrieve the pom.xml like this:\n\n  curl \"https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=policy/${PROJ}.git;a=blob_plain;f=pom.xml;hb=refs/heads/master\" >pom.xml\n\nWould also have to add \"-N -fn\" to the \"mvn\" line so it doesn't try to examine all of the modules.  Also remove the \"cd\" lines, as they would no longer be needed.",
